trans-unit.source: The ActiveDirectorySchema class represents the schema partition for a particular domain.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ActiveDirectorySchema representerer partisjonen skjemaet for et bestemt domene.

trans-unit.source: Releases the managed resources that are used by the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema"></xref> object and, optionally, releases unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir administrerte ressurser som brukes av den <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ActiveDirectorySchema"> </xref> objektet, og eventuelt versjoner uforvaltet ressurser.

trans-unit.source: The `disposing` parameter affects only the release of managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Den `disposing` parameteren påvirker bare utgave av administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: Unmanaged resources are always released by this method.
trans-unit.target: Ubehandlet ressurser frigis alltid av denne metoden.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false " name="false " href=""></xref>to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false " name="false " href=""> </xref>frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.
